**PROP-031 / REQ-002 rev8 / FIND-031 / Q5=A**:

- Removed: `if (markdown === "") return Ok([paragraph("")])` (empty-string fallback)
- Removed: `if (blocks.length === 0) blocks.push(paragraph(""))` (end-of-input guarantee)
